<HEADLINE>
RIGHT-WINGERS REVISE JAPAN'S HISTORY  
 
</HEADLINE>
   (This excellent ``separate buy'' article is from The Independent
newspaper in London.)  
  
 (To publish this article, it must be purchased from New York Times
Syndicate sales representative NIRDI RELIS in New York at
1-800-972-3550 or 212-499-3333, or fax her at 212-499-3382.)  
  
 (EDITORS: FOR THOSE DESIRING A SHORTER VERSION, THIS EASILY-CUT
ARTICLE STANDS IN 850 WORDS. TOTAL UNCUT VERSION RUNS 975.)  
  
 (PLEASE NOTE: This article has been transmitted twice _ into the
``i'' international news and ``k'' commentary news files.)  
  
 By RICHARD LLOYD PARRY  
 c.1998 The Independent, London  
 (Distributed by New York Times Special Features)  
