<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-12-01 13:45 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6762 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u w &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-OLIPHANT-COLUMN-BOS &LR;      12-01 0817
