<P>
   &UR; WASHINGTON (w) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   OLIPHANT-COLUMN (Washington) _ Where's the case against the
president? By Thomas Oliphant. &UR;  &LR; (w and k coding.)
</P>
<P>
   &UR;  &LR;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; NATIONAL (a) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   MISSING-TRIO (Orlando, Fla.) -- The absence of any clues, any
credible leads, and any evidence that three missing Massachusettts
men staged their own disappearance has anguished their large
families and baffled seasoned investigators. By Brian MacQuarrie.
(2 takes)
</P>
<P>
   MA-WELFARE (Boston) -- As the the official deadline for the
