   Cape Air _ yes, the very same airline that offers service to
Martha's Vineyard and Nantucket _ is now offering flights between
San Juan, Puerto Rico, and St. Thomas in the US Virgin Islands.
Cape Air also offers Florida service with flights to Key West from
Fort Lauderdale, Fort Myers, and Naples.
</P>
