House Democratic Leader, appealed to the Republican leadership to
``bring some order out of the chaos.'' By Alison Mitchell.
</P>
<P>
   FUNDRAISING-REPORT (Washington) _ A report by auditors for the
Federal Election Commission has concluded that President Clinton
and Republican presidential candidate Robert Dole violated election
spending limits during their primary campaigns and should be
required to repay millions of dollars. By Jill Abramson.
</P>
