   CHILDREN'S BOOKS-SPIRITUALITY &QL;
</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ Children's books can do more than entertain; they can
teach life lessons. Some books teach our children important Bible
stories in words they can understand. Others aren't strictly
religious, but can still be defined as spiritual. They explain the
need for sharing, understanding and loving thy neighbor, for
exhibiting kindness in unkind situations. By SANDY GUERRA-CLINE.
Story has moved in ``e'' entertainment category. &QL; 
