   Non-subscribers may make individual graphics purchases or get
additional information by calling the NYT Photo/Graphics desk at
(212) 556-4204 between noon and 10 p.m. EST.
</P>
<P>
   GENERAL
</P>
<P>
   AIDSVAX/Gp120 vaccine.clr -- 2 x 2 1/2 -- (BC-AIDSVAX-COX)
</P>
<P>
   FreeHand. Color chart explains how the AIDSVAX vaccine works.
</P>
<P>
   BUDDHA/Lumbini, Nepal map-- 1 x 1 3/4 --
(BC-BUDDHA-BIRTHPLACE-NYT)
</P>
<P>
