<P>
   HOSPITAL-RATINGS (Los Angeles) _ Health centers in L.A.'s San
Fernando Valley area rate well treating heart problems and
orthopedic disorders, but shine less bright when fighting cancer,
according to a private survey of Los Angeles hospitals. By Ben
Sullivan.
