   FURBY-CRAZE (Los Angeles) _ If you want Furbys, just about the
only places to find them are in the classifieds, online auctions,
where they are selling for $100 or more each _ or Earl Jacobsen's
L.A. garage. By Lee Condon. (Will move in the ``n'' California and
