Albright is backing a Canadian effort to keep an Alberta man from
being executed in Texas. Albright has written to state officials
asking for a stay in the execution of Stanley Faulder, condemned
for the 1975 murder of the elderly matriarch of a Texas oil family.
By JIM HENDERSON. (Already filed.)
