personal computer, you're within arm's reach of America's biggest
garage sale. Thousands of people who just don't have enough stuff
and don't want to leave home to get more have made on-line auction
site eBay the Internet's latest why-didn't-I-think-of-that
phenomenon. ``One man's junk is another man's treasure,'' said
Jennifer Chu, eBay's associate public relations manager. (Kalajian,
Palm Beach Post) MOVED.
