<DOCNO> NYT19981201.0434 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> MISCELLANEOUS TEXT (slug-filter) </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-12-01 21:27 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
