</P>
<P>
   ``Unquestionably, it will be the best (deal) in the NFL, and
probably the best in professional sports,'' said Dean Bonham,
president of the Bonham Group, a Denver sports marketing consulting
firm. ``But I'm skeptical of the assumptions, particularly in the
