   ``That's about $35,000 over the NFL average for suites,'' Bonham
said. ``You're talking about a market that is overbuilding by 50
the number of suites they should have ... and probably overpricing
them by $25,000 to $35,000 per suite.''
</P>
<P>
   But the report said the city could support the higher prices
