A7948 &Cx1f; tad-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-FBC-ALL-BIG-TEAM-COX     12-01 0597
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-FBC-ALL-BIG-TEAM-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Ricky Williams offensive player of the year in All-Big 12 Team
 &HT;    By Randy Riggs
 &HT;    c. 1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
